OOC: Oops, missed that post. The post about him going there, adn turning
it off are void. I'm taking up right after KitKat told him to go, check
it out.

::DrillBit::

He reached the bridge, to turn off the sound. As soon as he reached the
computer, it stoped. Someone els must have taken care of it.
Then KitKat's request came over the comm.
"Sure. I'll be right there." He replyed, walking off towards teh
conferance room. He arrived.
"Please follow me. I'll show you out." He said with a polite smile, to
Aracnia, and the other.

::Hot Rod::

He arrived at the base.
"Hot Rod, maximize." He transformed, and took the parts to the CR.
He knew she was gone, but it was all he could do. He just stood there
looking at the CR.
